sections.text:
(a) water – in which water is the sole packing medium; 
 (b) water and fruit juice – in which water and fruit juice(s) from the specified fruits, is the sole liquid packing medium; 
 (c) fruit juice – in which one or more fruit juice(s) from the specified fruits, which may be strained or filtered, is the sole liquid packing medium; or 
 (d) with sugar(s) – any of the foregoing packing media (a) through (c), may have one or more of the following sugars added: sucrose, invert sugar syrup, dextrose, dried glucose syrup, glucose syrup, fructose and fructose syrup.

